2018年9月6日，印度最高法院废除了普遍认为是对同性恋者不友善的“377条”。从这一天起，印度同性性行为不再属于违法。

'''女同性恋，男同性恋，双性恋和跨性别（[[LGBT|LGBT]]）'''人群曾在[[印度|印度]]面临着非[[LGBT|LGBT]]居民没有经历过的法律和社会困难。

在过去，同性之间的性行为是违法的，同性伴侣不能獲得结婚或伴侣上的法定身份关系。印度法律承认[[海吉拉|海吉拉]]是[[第三性别|第三性别]]，与男性或女性分开。2008年7月29日印度城市[[德里|德里]]，[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]和[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]举行了第一次同志游行。<ref name="lawyersclubindia.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.lawyersclubindia.com/articles/legal-status-of-homosexuality-in-india-170.asp|title=legal status of homosexuality in india|work=Lawyersclubindia|access-date=2016-11-30|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613000817/http://www.lawyersclubindia.com/articles/legal-status-of-homosexuality-in-india-170.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==关于LGBT的法律==
根据1860年《印度刑法》第377条，同性性交被定为刑事犯罪。2009年，德里高等法院裁决第377条违反《印度宪法》规定的基本权利。根据印度最高法院的裁决，高等法院关于法律的合宪性的决定适用于整个印度，而不仅仅适用于有关高等法院所管辖的国家领土。<ref name="Kusum Ingots v 2004">''Kusum Ingots v. Union of India'', (2004) 6 SCC 254: "An order passed on a writ petition questioning the constitutionality of a Parliamentary Act, whether interim or final, keeping in view the provisions contained in Clause (2) of Article 226 of the Constitution of India, will have effect throughout the territory of India subject of course to the applicability of the Act."</ref>2012年2月23日，内政部以印度社會的道德情感為由，表示反对同性性行为非刑事化。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-02-23/news/31091001_1_decriminalisation-judgement-hc|title=Centre opposes decriminalisation of homosexuality in SC|last=Mahapatra|first=Dhananjay|date=2012-02-23|work=Economic Times|publisher=Times Internet|accessdate=2014-09-09|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305022353/http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-02-23/news/31091001_1_decriminalisation-judgement-hc|dead-url=no}}</ref>中央政府于2012年2月28日扭转了立场，声称将同性性行为非罪化方面没有法律错误。这导致最高法院的两名法官谴责中央政府经常改变其在这个问题上的立场。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/supreme-court-pulls-up-centre-for-flipflop-on-homosexuality/917743|title=Supreme Court pulls up Centre for flip-flop on homosexuality|date=2012-02-28|work=The Indian Express|accessdate=2014-09-09|archive-date=2014-09-09|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140909211747/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/supreme-court-pulls-up-centre-for-flipflop-on-homosexuality/917743|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年12月11日，最高法院撤销了2009年德里高等法院对其管辖范围内自愿的同性性行为予以非刑事化的法令。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://barandbench.com/comment/44159#.UqifDPRDtrA|title=Supreme Court sets aside Delhi High Court judgment in Naz Foundation; Declares S.377 to be constitutional|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20131211173739/http://barandbench.com/comment/44159%23.UqifDPRDtrA#.UqifDPRDtrA|archivedate=2013-12-11|accessdate=2016-11-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=India's top court upholds law criminalising gay sex|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/10509952/Indias-top-court-upholds-law-criminalising-gay-sex.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2013-12-11|location=London|first=Dean|last=Nelson|date=2013-12-11|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903053827/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/10509952/Indias-top-court-upholds-law-criminalising-gay-sex.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Supreme Court makes gay sex punishable offence, again; Twitter war breaks out between those for and against the verdict|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-blow-to-gay-rights-activists-as-supreme-court-upholds-article-377-makes-gay-sex-punishable-offence-1933110|publisher=DNA India|accessdate=2013-12-11|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214042204/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-blow-to-gay-rights-activists-as-supreme-court-upholds-article-377-makes-gay-sex-punishable-offence-1933110|dead-url=no}}</ref>有法官指出，议会应该就此事进行辩论和决定。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/homosexuality-is-criminal-offence-supreme-court/articleshow/27210542.cms | title=Homosexuality is criminal offence: Supreme Court | publisher=''Economic Times'' | date=2013-12-11 | accessdate=2013-12-11 | archive-date=2019-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811023050/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/homosexuality-is-criminal-offence-supreme-court/articleshow/27210542.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年1月28日最高法院驳回了[[印度政府|中央政府]]，非政府组织纳兹基金会和其他几个机构提交的反对其12月11日对第377条的裁决的复审请愿书。<ref>{{cite web|title=Supreme Court refuses overruling its Verdict on Section 377 and Homosexuality|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/01/supreme-court-refuses-overruling-its-verdict-on-article-377-and-homosexuality/|work=IANS|publisher=Biharprabha News|accessdate=2014-01-28|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327032746/http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/01/supreme-court-refuses-overruling-its-verdict-on-article-377-and-homosexuality/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年4月，最高法院承认[[海吉拉|海吉拉]]等跨性別群體，是[[第三性别|第三性别]]，並要求政府給予平等的法律地位和保障<ref>{{cite news|title=India court recognises transgender people as third gender|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-27031180|agency=bbc|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2017-05-07|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209195343/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-27031180|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年12月18日，[[印度国民大会党|印度国民大会党]]成员沙希·塔鲁尔提交了第377条非刑罪化的法案，但该法案以71-24票被否决。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/world/regions/south-central-asia/116433-india-blocks-mp-vote-decriminalize-gay-sex|title=India parliament blocks MP's bill to decriminalize gay sex|work=Rappler|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629083130/https://www.rappler.com/world/regions/south-central-asia/116433-india-blocks-mp-vote-decriminalize-gay-sex|dead-url=no}}</ref>

人权团体表示担心这会使同性恋者受到警察的骚扰。<ref>{{cite news|author=Harmit Shah Singh|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/12/11/world/asia/india-same-sex-relationship/|title=India's Supreme Court declares homosexual sex illegal|work=CNN|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2019-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622201913/https://www.cnn.com/2013/12/11/world/asia/india-same-sex-relationship/|dead-url=no}}</ref>纳兹基金会表示他们将提出请愿书以审查法院的决定。<ref>{{cite news|title=Naz Foundation to file review petition against SC order on section 377|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-naz-foundation-to-file-review-petition-against-sc-order-on-section-377-1933374|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620021308/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-naz-foundation-to-file-review-petition-against-sc-order-on-section-377-1933374|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年2月2日，最高法院决定审查同性性行为的刑事定罪是否違憲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/indias-top-court-examine-gay-rights-36659702|title=ABC News|author=ABC News|work=ABC News|accessdate=2016-11-30|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202133515/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/indias-top-court-examine-gay-rights-36659702|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年，喀拉拉邦政府推出为跨性别者提供免费的性别重置手术的政策。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scroll.in/article/804496/why-keralas-free-sex-change-surgeries-will-offer-a-new-lifeline-for-the-transgender-community|title=Why Kerala’s free sex-change surgeries will offer a new lifeline for the transgender community|last=Devasia|first=TK|website=Scroll.in|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131063552/https://scroll.in/article/804496/why-keralas-free-sex-change-surgeries-will-offer-a-new-lifeline-for-the-transgender-community|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dnaindia.com">{{Cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-how-kerala-left-the-country-behind-on-transgender-rights-2145017|title=How Kerala left the country behind on transgender rights {{!}} Latest News & Updates at Daily News & Analysis|website=dna|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629021111/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-how-kerala-left-the-country-behind-on-transgender-rights-2145017|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年4月，印度的中央部會級機構，要求地方政府確保對跨性別人士的平等公民權，當中包括可按其性別認同使用公共廁所<ref>{{cite news|title=India allows transgender people choice in toilets|url=http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/en/component/k2/1323792-20170406.htm?spTabChangeable=0|date=2017-04-06}}</ref>。

2018年9月6日，印度最高法院做出历史性判决，推翻一殖民时期确立，已实施了近157年的同性性行为禁令，即“377条”。从这一天起，'''印度同性性行为不再违法。'''

